Multi-Scale Multi-Modal File Format for Neuroscience based on HDF5

NeuroHDF recommends a particular hierarchical layout of HDF5 and a minimal set
of metadata attributes for multi-scale and multi-modal requirements.

HDF5 Links
----------
* Main HDF Group page
http://www.hdfgroup.org/

* Python libraries
http://code.google.com/p/h5py/
